name: BUMP Poster
description:
A poster we peeled off from a London wall in 1999.
Fix yourself the price: another poster, plants, second hand vinyls, slides... or if you prefer to use money, we will sent it to a charity.

Since we are not making profit out of it, we only exchange items f2f.
To get your stuff, you'll need to come to Portaferrissa, 25, Barcelona.
And if you want, we can show you La Casa and take a picture of you for our blog :-) :-)

name: Our old HP Color LaserJet 2600
description:
Fix yourself the price: another machine, a plant, second hand vinyls, slides... or if you prefer to use money, we will sent it to a charity.

Since we are not making profit out of it, we only exchange items f2f.
To get your stuff, you'll need to come to Portaferrissa, 25, Barcelona.
And if you want, we can show you La Casa and take a picture of you for our blog :-) :-)



MORE INFO:

Ha empezado a manchar las hojas cada poco tiempo, y desde HP nos marearon mil veces diciendo que es cuestión de limpieza y de cambio de toners, que nos pasa por usar tóners no originales y blah blah.

Ahora toca comprar toner amarillo que está agotado (los otros tres están a la mitad) y como nos salió una superoferta para una Canon, hemos decidido dar salida a ésta.

Se adjunta factura del 07.07.08 para garantía.
